s parents and Howard's girlfriend, Mary, who see this trip as just another impetuously stupid idea by flaky George. Howard has to try and reconcile all these competing forces in his life.  —Huggo","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.4084,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"1957-01-01","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Howard","original_language":"en"},{"id":661486,"adult":false,"title":"Porttikielto taivaaseen","video":false,"overview":"High-class prostitute Bella works for hotel manager TT with Sara, Lulu and Cindy. However, Bella misses the ordinary life and love of her youth Timo, who is a hockey player on the team owned by TT.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.5651,"vote_count":7,"poster_path":"/wUzA0JgGup2BOb2tQhtwKxyerNY.jpg","release_date":"1990-03-30","vote_average":3.5,"backdrop_path":"/nufvT1quuw9TepBDWO9Yw3mIXat.jpg","original_title":"Porttikielto taivaaseen","original_language":"fi"},{"id":277369,"adult":false,"title":"Hail, Hero!","video":false,"overview":"Carl Dixon decides to quit school and enlist in the Army, even though he's already run afoul of the law as a Vietnam protestor. It is our hero's intention to use love, rather than bullets, to combat the Viet Cong. Needless to say, his idealism is no match for the harsher realities of war.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.2319,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/kyhiTr5YiNg2d5lrLyXrq4KsICi.jpg","release_date":"1969-10-04","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/mQtq4Ajct42GvbAcXrGPdXx3es7.jpg","original_title":"Hail, Hero!","original_language":"en"},{"id":1067485,"adult":false,"title":"Sebastian","video":false,"overview":"Max is a 25-year-old freelance writer and aspiring novelist who seems well on his way to success in London’s cultural spheres. Yet by night, he finds a different kind of exhilaration as a sex worker with the pseudonym Sebastian, meeting men via an escorting platform. Max uses his experiences as Sebastian to fuel his stories and the worthy debut novel that he has been longing to write, finally seems within reach.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.2755,"vote_count":47,"poster_path":"/22JTGme2MLETmvhHQdiKP78S5Qf.jpg","release_date":"2024-08-02","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/kEvBFfqCtJvtvwZcrprAT3dSvij.jpg","original_title":"Sebastian","original_language":"en"},{"id":470861,"adult":false,"title":"Liza, Liza, Skies Are Grey","video":false,"overview":"A teenage girl and her boyfriend set off on an eventful road trip up the coast of California hoping to figure out the meaning of love and life.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.4886,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/54XDVjXruiusiTKLIMzNr1q89C.jpg","release_date":"2016-09-17","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":"/lbYjniPOnwdPXFpw4gOQ0VwzgiW.jpg","original_title":"Liza, Liza, Skies Are Grey","original_language":"en"},{"id":470901,"adult":false,"title":"Face 2 Face","video":false,"overview":"Over a series of video chats, a teenage outcast reaches out to his childhood friend, but finds that behind the veneer of popularity and a seemingly perfect life, she hides a disturbing secret.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.3045,"vote_count":43,"poster_path":"/lciZWx3qVPUxGnw9rzNBqNgQPuN.jpg","release_date":"2017-04-23","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/9VoU9AV6POqPSVXVR832BZDBAr.jpg","original_title":"Face 2 Face","original_language":"en"},{"id":661781,"adult":false,"title":"Heatwave","video":false,"overview":"The tense relationship between a mother and son reaches a climax during a summer heatwave.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.6913,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/qdecMfnbQhs186tzJD0FlrurzhA.jpg","release_date":"2021-12-21","vote_average":1,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Heatwave","original_language":"en"},{"id":8967,"adult":false,"title":"The Tree of Life","video":false,"overview":"The impressionistic story of a Texas family in the 1950s. The film follows the life journey of the eldest son, Jack, through the innocence of childhood to his disillusioned adult years as he tries to reconcile a complicated relationship with his father. Jack finds himself a lost soul in the modern world, seeking answers to the origins and meaning of life while questioning the existence of faith.","genre_ids":[18,14],"popularity":2.946,"vote_count":3278,"poster_path":"/l8cwuB5WJSoj4uMAsnzuHBOMaSJ.jpg","release_date":"2011-05-17","vote_average":6.727,"backdrop_path":"/xq1HIwZq9VbuvMQELAua1nqEkH.jpg","original_title":"The Tree of Life","original_language":"en"},{"id":8992,"adult":false,"title":"The Sure Thing","video":false,"overview":"Gib, a beer-guzzling slob, and Alison, an uptight Ivy-Leaguer, are an unlikely duo stuck together on a cross-country trip during Christmas break. At first they get on each other's nerves but, as time passes, they find their divergent natures complement each other. Now they need to realize what they've already found before it's too late.","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"popularity":1.6926,"vote_count":314,"poster_path":"/a9cuohQn5kczi4htWZAZjEZvXkZ.jpg","release_date":"1985-03-01","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/aTiarj2HriXg3EQROAuyRvHlf0V.jpg","original_title":"The Sure Thing","original_language":"en"},{"id":8896,"adult":false,"title":"Delta","video":false,"overview":"A man comes home to meet his mother and sister after many years away. He finds his mother living with a new boyfriend, and his sister to be grown-up. He begins to settle down in this new place by building a new home for himself on the delta. But when his sister moves in with him and the two begin a romance, there are tragic consequences.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.3111,"vote_count":20,"poster_path":"/qXfD0rh8kec7FTsPuf9L6iYGlJN.jpg","release_date":"2008-09-11","vote_average":5.2,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Delta","original_language":"hu"},{"id":861691,"adult":false,"title":"Albion Rose","video":false,"overview":"Following the arrival of an unwanted guest, the tightly-knit bond between two sisters is put to the test when their idyllic playdate takes a dark turn. Supported by The Future of Film is Female, ALBION ROSE is a late bloomer's coming-of-age drama with hints of magical realism and dark fairytale elements that paint a delicate, yet emotionally charged portrait of sisterhood, loss, and the healing powers of fantasy.","genre_ids":[18,14],"popularity":0.2389,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/4I57BXY0k9E0U3Huwk8krXag2HY.jpg","release_date":"2023-04-05","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Albion Rose","original_language":"en"},{"id":8772,"adult":false,"title":"The Last Day","video":false,"overview":"At Christmas time, 19-year-old Simon returns home to visit his dysfunctional family with Louise, a fearless girl he met during his train ride. While Simon struggles to cope with the growing distance between him and his parents, he starts to examine his feelings when Louise develop a liaison of her own with his childhood friend Mathieu.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.2119,"vote_count":28,"poster_path":"/rbFoWHvaAoJvy17ZUZC5401Uec2.jpg","release_date":"2004-11-03","vote_average":4.554,"backdrop_path":"/ueIUTn3HpeWgyelKBjgQBblDt0Y.jpg","original_title":"Le dernier jour","original_language":"fr"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt0083552","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q474006","instagram_id":null,"mydramalist_id":"91761","rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/love_strange_love"},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":148611,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"BR","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"pt","descriptors":[],"release_date":"1982-01-11T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"US","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"1982-07-07T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]}],"aggregate_credits":null,"origi